{
  "stem": "15694.10",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told me again stories from Auschwitz like a certain person in Auschwitz-- I only remember one name, and I remembered it later again.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I came across it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The name was Boga.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] had a contraption in his office, the so-called Boga swing, where he stripped prisoners, put them-- hung them up like an airplane, and with sticks-- maybe on the body and often on the genitals-- hit them to make them fly.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the invitation given out for the nearby officers and ladies, so-called ladies, SS women to come in and look at the performance.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, one such person spoke to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were sad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They said I am finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I won't survive it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Remember me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Remember my name, and he told me the name, but I haven't remembered it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remembered Boga, the name of Boga of the SS men, and the men later.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I think in, in Frankfurt, there was the not the Nuremberg Process.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was another one in Frankfurt-- Auschwitz Process.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this Boga was then, I sort of, I think, a pretty good life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Of course, he wasn't guilty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Somebody else did all of the killing and what ever he did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But that's-- I wanted to sort of switch from that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And while he was still talking, the train stopped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we went out to a place which in my English version I called the [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Hard ?] Mountains, the camp, and somewhere in the [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Hard ?] Mountains because I forgot the name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "On a couple or three years ago or so in Germany, somebody said, I'm going on holiday to Osterode.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I had a, that was the name where we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
